description: Cam Christou"The Cannon"Ht: 5'10"Wt: 170lbsSeason W/L Record (0-0)Chris Bines"Mr. Badass"Ht: 5'10"Wt: 180lbsSeason W/L Record (1-0) Back after a ferocious victory against Leon "The Masticator" Fox we have "Mr. Badass" Chris Bines. title: Cam "The Cannon" Christou vs Chris "Mr. Badass" Bines
